text: Lorn may refer to: ==Places== * Lorn, New South Wales, a suburb of Maitland, New South Wales, Australia *Firth of Lorn, body of water off Scotland *Lorn Rocks, rocks in Antarctica *An alternate spelling for Lorne, Scotland ==People== * Lorn (musician), an American electronic musician * Lorn Brown (c.1938 - 2010), American sports broadcaster * Lorn, the mate of Tragg in Tragg and the Sky Gods mid-1970s comic book ==See also== * * Lorne (disambiguation)
